line_1: And lodges but in gentle breasts,
line_2: Love, who the cruel mind detests,

line_1: Wi' kindling fury i' their breasts,
line_2: They'll talk o' patronage an' priests,

line_1: And blackens each fair image in our breasts.
line_2: Yet e'en those joys dire Jealousy molests,

line_1: By Goodness prompted, native of their Breasts,
line_2: Sir Harry and my Lady were my Guests.
